OL,4,G0210FLily & Lolly: The Forgotten Yeats
OL,5,     FSisters
OL,6,     GImelda May explores the legacy of
OL,7,     GSusan and Elizabeth Yeats, two
OL,8,     Gsisters who played a significant
OL,9,     Grole in the revival of Irish
OL,10,     Gliterature in the 1920s.
OL,11,G0335FStories From The National
OL,12,     FPortrait Gallery
OL,13,     GKate Bryan explores 20th-century
OL,14,     Gportraiture, examining depictions
OL,15,     Gof war poets and Queen Elizabeth
OL,16,     GII. Jim Moir drops in to discuss
OL,17,     Ghis favourite work.
